    "title": "Opening for Software Engineer at ISRO Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Software Engineer looking for your next big career move? ISRO Advisory Limited in Vadodara offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout ISRO Advisory Limited:\nISRO Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Docker\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Referral bonus program\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ISRO Advisory Limited!",
